10110.description: Spellbook needed to learn Meteor. Can be used by an Arch Mage and a Soul Taker. Can be acquired at level 81.

10111.name: Forgotten Scroll - Star Fall
10111.description: Spellbook needed to learn Star Fall. Can be used by a Mystic Muse and a Storm Screamer. Can be acquired at level 81.

10112.name: Dark Seed
10112.description: Item needed for the Imbue Dark Seed Skill. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

10113.name: Special Bolt
10113.description: Item needed for the Deadly Roulette, and Bleeding Shot skills. It cannot be exchanged or dropped.

10114.name: Sealed Dynasty Sigil Piece
10114.description: Ingredient needed for a Dwarf to make a Dynasty Sigil. It can be sold to public stores.

10115.name: Recipe: Sealed Dynasty Sigil (60%)
10115.description: For Dwarves only. The recipe for the Sealed Dynasty Sigil. Requires Create Item Skill - Level 9. 60% success rate.

10116.name: Recipe: Sealed Dynasty Sigil (100%)
10116.description: Exclusive to Dwarves. Recipe for making a Sealed Dynasty Sigil. Requires Create Item - Skill Level 9. The success rate is 100%.

10117.name: Chaotic Sealed Dynasty Sigil
10117.description: A rare Sealed Dynasty Sigil that requries a thorough varnishing. It can be varnished by the Blacksmith of Mammon.

10118.name: Chaotic Dynasty Sigil
10118.description: A rare Sealed Dynasty Sigil that requires a thorough varnishing. It can be varnished by the Blacksmith of Mammon.

10119.name: Dynasty Sigil
10119.description: Increases M. Def. and Resistance to Dark. Dynasty Sigil

10120.name: Sealed Dynasty Sigil
10120.description: Sealed Masterwork Item. Seal can be removed by the Blacksmith of Mammon or Maestro Ishuma.

10121.name: Sealed Arcana Sigil
10121.description: Sealed Masterwork Item. The seal can be broken with the help of the Blacksmith of Mammon.

10122.name: Red Crescent Earring
10122.description: Cannot be exchanged, dropped, crystallized, or enchanted

10123.name: Necklace of Devotion
10123.description: Cannot be exchanged, dropped, crystallized, or enchanted.

10124.name: Ring of Devotion
10124.description: Cannot be exchanged, dropped, crystallized, or enchanted.

10125.name: Shadow Item - War Axe
10125.description: A Shadow Item with the power of a War Axe. It cannot be traded, dropped, crystallized, or given other functions.

10126.name: Dynasty Leather Armor - Force Master
10126.description: Can only be worn by Duelists and Grand Khavataris.

10127.name: Dynasty Leather Armor - Weapon Master
10127.description: Can only be worn by Dreadnoughts, Titans, Fortune Seekers, Maestros, Doombringers and Soul Hounds.

10129.name: Scroll of Escape: Fortress
10129.description: A magical scroll that transports you to your Fortress. If you don't have a Fortress, it will relocate you to the nearest village. Scroll of Fortress Return

10130.name: Blessed Scroll of Escape: Fortress
10130.description: A magical scroll that transports you to your Fortress quickly. Blessed Scroll of Fortress Return

10131.name: Transformation Scroll: Onyx Beast
10131.description: A Scroll that transforms you into an Onyx Beast for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Onyx Beast

10132.name: Transformation Scroll: Death Blader
10132.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Death Blader for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Death Blader

10133.name: Transformation Scroll: Grail Apostle
10133.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Grail Apostle for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Grail Apostle

10134.name: Transformation Scroll: Unicorn
10134.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Unicorn for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Unicorn

10135.name: Transformation Scroll: Lilim Knight
10135.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Lilim Knight for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Lilim Knight

10136.name: Transformation Scroll: Golem Guardian
10136.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Golem Guardian for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Golem Guardian

10137.name: Transformation Scroll: Inferno Drake
10137.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Inferno Drake for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Inferno Drake

10138.name: Transformation Scroll: Dragon Bomber
10138.description: A Scroll that transforms you into a Dragon Bomber for 30 minutes. Transformation Sealbook: Dragon Bomber

10139.name: Agathion Bracelet
10139.description: A bracelet that summons a cute Rainbow Clan Hall Agathion. Shadow Item that cannot be exchanged or dropped. It lasts for 700 minutes. Performing Agathion - Rainbow Clan Hall

10140.name: Blessed Ring of Escape
10140.description: Makes Blessed Scroll of Escape available for up to 250 minutes, with a 60-second recharge for Escape. Only one effect is applied, even if you wear 2 identical rings. Blessed Ring of Escape

10141.name: Grey Talisman - Yeti Transform
10141.description: Can be transformed into a Yeti for a certain amount of time. Transformation is cancelled if unequipped. Effect does not stack with additional Talismans of the same type. This item cannot be traded or dropped. Transform Yeti

10142.name: Grey Talisman - Buffalo Transform
10142.description: Can be transformed into a Buffalo for a certain amount of time. Transformation is cancelled if unequipped. Effect does not stack with additional Talismans of the same type. This item cannot be traded or dropped. Transform Buffalo

10143.name: Battleground Spell - Shield Master
10143.description: Effects of Wind Walk Lv 2, Shield Lv 3, Magic Barrier Lv 2, Bless Shield Lv 6, and Haste Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Wind

10144.name: Battleground Spell - Wizard
10144.description: Effects of Wind Walk Lv 2, Shield Lv 3, Magic Barrier Lv 2, Acumen Lv 1, and Empower Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Wind

10145.name: Battleground Spell - Healer
10145.description: Effects of Wind Walk Lv 2, Shield Lv 3, Magic Barrier Lv 2, Acumen Lv 1, and Heal Empower Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Wind

10146.name: Battleground Spell - Dagger Master
10146.description: Effects of Wind Walk Lv 2, Might Lv 3, Magic Barrier Lv 2, Focus Lv 1, and Haste Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Wind

10147.name: Battleground Spell - Bow Master
10147.description: Effects of Wind Walk Lv 2, Might Lv 3, Magic Barrier Lv 2, Guidance Lv 1, and Haste Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Wind

10148.name: Battleground Spell - Berserker
10148.description: Effects of Berserker Spirit Lv 2 and Clarity Lv 1 can be obtained for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Berserker Spirit

10149.name: Battleground Blessed Scroll of Escape
10149.description: Relocates you to the nearest village. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Blessed Scroll of Battlefield Escape

10150.name: Battleground Blessed Scroll of Resurrection
10150.description: Resurrects a dead character and restores his or her Exp. completely. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Blessed Scroll of Battlefield Resurrection

10151.name: Battleground Transform Spell
10151.description: When used, it transforms you into a pixy for a certain amount of time. It can only be used on the battleground during a siege battle or a fortress battle. It will have no effect if used while in a transformed state. Scroll of Battlefield Transformation

10152.name: Battle Health Recovery Potion
10152.description: Recovers HP when in use. Characters below Level 52 are not affected. Usable only during a Siege or Fortress war. Lesser Battlefield Healing Potion

10153.name: Battle Mana Recovery Potion
10153.description: Recovers MP when in use. Characters below Level 52 are not affected. Usable only during a Siege or Fortress war. Lesser Battlefield Mana Potion

10154.name: Battle CP Recovery Potion
10154.description: Recovers CP when in use. Characters below Level 52 are not affected. Usable only during a Siege or Fortress war. Lesser Battlefield CP Potion

10155.name: Mental Strengthening Potion
10155.description: Increases Resistance to Hold and Sleep for a certain period of time. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Mental Potion

10156.name: Medusa's Potion
10156.description: Becomes invincible temporarily. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Medusa Potion

10157.name: Instant Haste Potion
10157.description: Increases Speed instantly. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Instant Haste Potion

10158.name: Grey Talisman of Upper Grade Fishing
10158.description: Obtains Upper-Grade Fishing Mastery Level (Lv 24). Effect does not stack with additional Talismans of the same type. This item cannot be traded or dropped. Grey Talisman of Fishing

10159.name: Capture Rope
10159.description: Disturbs movement of targets. Can only be used in Siege and Fortress war. Capture Rope

10160.name: Cursed Red Soul Crystal - Stage 14
10160.description: A red crystal that is cursed by the darkness, stage 14. Take this to Legendary Blacksmith Shadai in Hellbound to process. Soul Crystal

10161.name: Cursed Blue Soul Crystal - Stage 14
10161.description: A blue crystal that is cursed by the darkness, stage 14. Take this to Legendary Blacksmith Shadai in Hellbound to process. Soul Crystal

10162.name: Cursed Green Soul Crystal - Stage 14
10162.description: A green crystal that is cursed by the darkness, stage 14. Take this to Legendary Blacksmith Shadai in Hellbound to process. Soul Crystal

10163.name: Wolf Collar
10163.description: Necklace used to summon wolves. It takes away some experience points the Pet Master earns. Wolf's Necklace

10164.name: Animal Slayer's List
10164.description: Destroys the animal slayers of the Mimir Forest, the Crimson Spiders.

10165.name: Bloody Red Claw
10165.description: A claw dripping with animal blood. Collect 50 of these and take them to Martin, the Pet Manager of the Town of Gludin.

10166.name: Hot Springs CP Potion
10166.description: Instantly recovers 1000 CP when used. Spring CP Potion

10167.name: Pig Lollipop
10167.description: Magic lollipop with a cute piggy drawing on it. Upon a strike, it makes a piggy noise. One can be transformed into a cute piggy for a certain amount of time. Exchange and drop are not available for this item which can be stored in a personal warehouse. Active Skill: Transform Pig

10168.name: Dynasty Leather Armor - Enchanter
10168.description: Can only be worn by Hierophants, Dominators, Doom Cryers and Judicators.

10169.name: Enchanter Circlet (Kamael only)
10169.description: A circlet that can be worn by the Kamael Race only, exclusively for the Enchanter class after completion of 2nd or 3rd class transfer. Cannot be worn in a sub job condition. Uses 2 hair accessory slots.

10171.name: Seed: Dark Coda
10171.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Aden area and it will bear the fruit of the Dark Coda. For best results, a level 5-15 character must plant it on a level 5-15 monster. Sowing

10172.name: Seed: Red Coda
10172.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Aden area and it will bear the fruit of the Red Coda. For best results, a level 8-18 character must plant it on a level 8-18 monster. Sowing

10173.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Aden area and it will bear the fruit of the Chilly Coda. For best results, a level 11-21 character must plant it on a level 11-21 monster. Sowing

10174.description: Plant this seed onto a monster in the Aden area and it will bear the fruit of the Blue Coda. For best results, a level 14-24 character must plant it on a level 14-24 monster. Sowing

10175.name: Goblin Circlet (Event)
10175.description: Gold colored, Goblin shaped hair accessory. This item is designed for use in events only and cannot be exchanged or dropped.

10176.name: White Half Mask
10176.description: A mysterious costume accessory that covers half of the wearer s face. This item cannot be traded or dropped.

10177.name: Black Half Mask
10177.description: A mysterious black mask. Don t you wish you knew where you could find the other half? This item cannot be traded or dropped. 4th Anniversary commemorative item.

10178.name: Sweet Fruit Cocktail
10178.description: A Cocktail made of various rare fruits. When consumed, it bestows temporary effects of Might, Shield, Wind Walk, Focus, Death Whisper, Guidance, Bless Shield, Bless Body, Haste, and Vampiric Rage for a certain amount of time. Might

10179.name: Fresh Fruit Cocktail
10179.description: A Cocktail made of various rare fruits. When consumed, it bestows temporary effects of Berserker Spirit, Blessed Body, Magic Barrier, Shield, Wind Walk, Blessed Soul, Empower, Acumen, and Clarity effects for a certain amount of time. Berserker Spirit
